  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for climate-friendly passive asset management&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;Adasina Social Capital mobilizes investors to drive long-term impact through industry campaigns and education. They center the voices of communities most impacted to leverage investments to pursue climate justice. Adasina will catalyze an industry-wide shift in the relationship between asset managers and the climate data that influences investment decisions. The two primary goals are to (1) partner with impacted communities to identify, source, and disseminate data regarding the most harmful aspects of the industrial food system and its impact on climate change and (2) educate and empower asset owners, asset managers, and financial gatekeepers to use this more relevant data set. (Sub-strategy: Climate Finance)&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
